data.text:
A message to our families regarding the Covid-19 pandemic

Paul Ippolito Memorial Welcomes You

Since 1900 four generations of our family has served the communities of Berkeley Heights, Summit, Caldwell, Orange, New Providence, Chatham, Warren, North Caldwell, West Caldwell, Essex Fells, Long Hill Township, Short Hills, Springfield, Roseland, Madison, Union, West Orange, Livingston and their surrounding areas. We're dedicated to continuing that tradition of which we are so proud. We are a small, family-owned business committed to working closely with the families we serve to fulfill and accommodate their individual needs and desires regarding the funeral services of their loved ones. We realize that many people are not familiar with making funeral arrangements, so we have designed this website to be used as an information guide. The information within our site is designed to answer some of the questions you may have regarding at-need funeral arrangements, pre-need funeral planning, and cremation services. We hope you find this website informative. For immediate assistance, please contact your desired location.
